###  https://cdm.ovh/rsm/localisation/loca#Rear
loca:Rear rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                   loca:SideEnum ;
          rdfs:label "Behind"@en .


###  https://cdm.ovh/rsm/localisation/loca#Right
